UMPS-complex
UMPS (UMP synthase complex) is a complex consisting of orotate phosphoribosyltransferase (OPRT) and OMP decarboxylase (OMPDC)

CAD-complex
CAD is a complex formed by carbamoyl phosphate synthethase 2 (CPS2), aspartate carbamoyltransferase (ACT) and digydroorotase (DHO)
